verbose_text: Galectin-8 is extensively expressed in normal tissues (brain, breast, large intestine, retina, kidney, pancreas, placenta, spleen, testicle, uterus, blood vessel, esophagus and heart), and it is also distributed in cancer tissues (brain, breast, large intestine, germ cells, head and neck, kidney, muscles, ovary, pancreas, thyroid gland, placenta, prostate, uterus, lung, stomach and esophagus cancer).
